(8, 1, 'Plan d\'orientation stratégique', NULL, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 115%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-bidi; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-bidi;\">Introduction au Plan d&rsquo;Orientation Strat&eacute;gique&nbsp;:</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-bidi; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-bidi;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 15.0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 115%; background: white;\"><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-bidi; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-bidi; color: black;\">Dans le cadre de la pr&eacute;paration du Plan d\'Orientation Strat&eacute;gique de l&rsquo;&eacute;tablissement, notre ambition est de forger une institution d\'excellence, capable de r&eacute;pondre aux d&eacute;fis actuels et futurs dans les domaines des </span><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-bidi; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-bidi;\">technologies avanc&eacute;es<span style=\"color: black;\">. Guid&eacute;s par des valeurs telles que</span> : l&rsquo;Engagement, la Solidarit&eacute;, la Transparence, l&rsquo;Appartenance, la Bienveillance, l&rsquo;&eacute;quit&eacute;, le partage, l&rsquo;excellence, le respect, l&rsquo;innovation, l&rsquo;accompagnement, la responsabilit&eacute;, et la pers&eacute;v&eacute;rance. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 15.0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 115%; background: white;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><u><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-bidi; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-bidi;\">ENSTAB</span></u></strong><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-bidi; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-bidi;\"> :<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><u>EN</u></strong>gagement-<strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><u>S</u></strong>olidarit&eacute;-<strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><u>T</u></strong>ransparence-<strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><u>A</u></strong>ppartenance-<strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><u>B</u></strong>ienveillance</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 115%; background: white; margin: 15.0pt 0cm 15.0pt 0cm;\"><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-bidi; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-bidi; color: black;\">Notre Plan d\'Orientation Strat&eacute;gique pour la p&eacute;riode 2023-2028 repose sur</span><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-bidi; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-bidi; color: red;\"> t</span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-bidi; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-bidi;\">rois piliers fondamentaux : le partenariat, l\'innovation et la responsabilit&eacute; sociale</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 115%; background: white; margin: 15.0pt 0cm 15.0pt 0cm;\"><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-bidi; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-bidi; color: black;\">Notre objectif est de cr&eacute;er un espace de libert&eacute; propice &agrave; la construction d\'une soci&eacute;t&eacute; instruite, prosp&egrave;re et &eacute;quitable.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 8.0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 107%;\"><a name=\"_heading=h.8sbbthu2x7ed\"></a><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-bidi; mso-fareast-font-family: Cambria; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-bidi;\">La mise en &oelig;uvre r&eacute;ussie de la strat&eacute;gie de l&rsquo;ENSTAB d&eacute;pend fortement de l\'implication et de la collaboration de tous les intervenants au sein de l\'&eacute;tablissement. Cela inclut les &eacute;tudiants, les enseignants, les chercheurs, le personnel administratif, les anciens &eacute;l&egrave;ves et les partenaires ext&eacute;rieurs.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 115%; background: white; margin: 15.0pt 0cm 15.0pt 0cm;\"><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-bidi; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-bidi; color: black;\">Le Plan d\'Orientation Strat&eacute;gique de l&rsquo;&eacute;tablissement est une boussole pr&eacute;cieuse qui oriente nos choix et nos actions. Il nous permet d\'anticiper les d&eacute;fis futurs avec confiance et d&eacute;termination. En suivant ce plan, nous sommes convaincus que nous b&acirc;tissons les fondations d\'une institution prestigieuse et innovante, contribuant activement au d&eacute;veloppement de la soci&eacute;t&eacute; et jouant un r&ocirc;le majeur dans la vie culturelle et artistique du pays.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 115%; background: white; margin: 15.0pt 0cm 15.0pt 0cm;\"><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-bidi; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-bidi; color: black;\">&Agrave; travers notre propre Plan d\'Orientation Strat&eacute;gique, nous nous alignons sur la vision de l\'Universit&eacute; </span><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-bidi; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-bidi;\">de Carthage <span style=\"color: black;\">et nous capitalisons sur la sp&eacute;cificit&eacute; de l\'enseignement </span>sup&eacute;rieur<span style=\"color: black;\"> en g&eacute;n&eacute;ral et dans notre &eacute;tablissement en particulier. Nos axes d&rsquo;orientation Strat&eacute;gique sont les suivants :</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: 74.7pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1; background: white;\"><!--