ves.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 115%; margin: 12.0pt 0cm 12.0pt 0cm;\"><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-bidi; mso-fareast-font-family: Cambria; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-bidi;\">Sur le plan sportif, un terrain multifonction a &eacute;t&eacute; am&eacute;nag&eacute;, un &eacute;quipement sportif sera mis &agrave; disposition des &eacute;tudiants et des &eacute;quipes sportives seront constitu&eacute;es. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 115%; margin: 12.0pt 0cm 12.0pt 0cm;\"><a name=\"_heading=h.6ckpvgu98kpg\"></a><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-bidi; mso-fareast-font-family: Cambria; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-bidi;\">Des espaces seront am&eacute;nag&eacute;s pour recevoir les clubs de l&rsquo;&eacute;cole et du mat&eacute;riel sera mis &agrave; disposition afin d&rsquo;encourager leurs activit&eacute;s et leur dynamisme.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 115%;\"><a name=\"_heading=h.gjdgxs\"></a><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-bidi; mso-fareast-font-family: Cambria; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-bidi; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-bidi;\">&nbsp;</span></p>', NULL, 'plan-d-orientation-strategique', NULL, NULL, 'INACTIVE', '2023-04-19 13:12:05', '2024-02-18 11:19:20', NULL, '1', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
